                     <interp inst="t17760911-75-off366" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing seven yards of linen cloth, value 15 s. a man's hat, value 5 s. a pair of silk stockings, value 2 s. four crown pieces, one silver milk pot, value 15 s. three gold rings, value 10 s. three pair of steel snuffers, value 2 s. a gold hat button, value 1 d. a gold hat loop, value 1 d. and a watch case made of metal, value 1 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17760911-75-person799">
                        William
                         Fearne
                     <interp inst="t17760911-75-person799" type="surname" value="Fearne"></interp>
