                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I keep a hardware shop in Moorfields; I bought three pair of steel snuffers of a man like the prisoner; I cannot swear he is the man.</p>
               <p>[They were produced in Court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.]</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I took the hat by mistake; I know nothing of the other things.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17760911-75-verdict369" type="verdictDescription">
